      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "We are starting in the GitHub Copilot app so the rest of the demo has some context. At the top level, you can see the main places people work here: Home, My Work, Automations, and Chat. This is the environment where the first invoice-review proof of concept was built and tested before we moved into the broader flow.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the GitHub Copilot app. Briefly orient the viewer to the environment and call out that this is a local or simulated POC.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111553_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.15.31@2x.png"
    },
    {
