      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "Once you are inside the project, the POC becomes more concrete. These areas show how the work is organized: chat to steer the task, actions to run steps, and canvas to shape the agent itself. We are still in a local or simulated setup here, but this is where the invoice-review idea starts to take form.",
      "demo_actions": "Click through Home, My Work, Automations, and Chat. Keep each stop brief.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111704_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.16.25@2x.png",
      "design_plan": "Narrative goal: frame the GitHub Copilot app as a simple top-level control bar with four clear surfaces the presenter clicks through quickly. Hero metaphor: a polished navigation runway, where four destination cards sit along a left-to-right path and one active focus glow moves across them. Main objects: (1) title and subtitle centered at top, (2) a thin top navigation rail spanning the upper-middle canvas, (3) four large destination cards labeled Home, My Work, Automations, and Chat arranged horizontally across the center with Home and My Work on the left half and Automations and Chat on the right half, (4) a subtle bottom caption line reading build, test, inspect to reinforce purpose, (5) three slim connector arrows between the cards to suggest brief click-through progression. Use CutReady tokens: $background for scene, $title for title, $subtitle for subtitle, $surface for cards, $border for rail and card outlines, $accent for the active emphasis and arrows, $foreground for main labels, $muted for secondary micro-labels. Motion beats: beat 1 title/subtitle fade in; beat 2 navigation rail and first card appear; beat 3 cards reveal left-to-right with a slight upward translate; beat 4 accent highlight shifts across the four cards in sequence, each card briefly scaling or brightening to imply the presenter clicking through surfaces; hold on all four visible and balanced. Keep it presentation-grade, minimal, and readable with about 12-18 total elements."
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
        "time": false,
        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
