      "time": "~40s",
      "narrative": "Here is the first invoice-review agent. It is set up to compare invoice lines with contract language and supporting operating records using a local model and MXC. The job is narrow on purpose: review what was billed against what was contracted, delivered, released, and approved.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the canvas. Show the agent configuration, model choice, and MXC setup. Point to the task definition or prompt if visible.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_112228_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.18.47@2x.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
        "time": false,
        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~40s",
      "narrative": "When we run it, the agent follows the same reasoning we carry forward into the rest of the demo. It checks local or simulated contracts, receipts, batch records, quality status, milestone approvals, and invoice lines, then returns a recommendation with supporting evidence. That becomes the foundation for what you will see next in Waypoint.",
      "demo_actions": "Run the agent on a sample invoice. Show inputs, tool or record access, and the resulting recommendation with cited evidence.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_112332_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.20.07@2x.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
