      },
      "time": "",
      "narrative": "Emphasize all of this review is happening with a local model, not cloud, and every document was read inside a Microsoft MXC sandbox. Show the canvas interacting with the session chat where the session explains what MXC prevented here.",
      "demo_actions": "Point at the green **🛡 Sandboxed** bar — \"every document was read inside a Microsoft MXC sandbox.\"",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_112324_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.20.38@2x.png"
    },
