      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "So the POC proves the task is viable. We can show the core invoice-review logic working locally, with clear evidence and safety controls around it. Next, we move into Waypoint to show how this idea expands into a fuller operating view with enterprise data, approvals, and production-ready controls.",
